督促公安机关撤销训诫书并追究有关人员责任2020年2月7日，国家监委成立调查组，就群众反映的涉及李文亮医生的有关情况依法开展调查。
Urging the public security organs to withdraw the reprimand and hold the personnel responsible On February 7, 2020, the NNSC set up an investigation team to investigate according to law the situation reported by the public concerning Dr. Li Wenliang.
现将调查情况通报如下。
The survey is reported below.
一、李文亮医生基本情况和转发、发布有关微信信息的背景及过程李文亮，男，满族，1985年10月出生，辽宁锦州人，中共党员，工作中因感染新型冠状病毒引发肺炎于2020年2月7日不幸去世，生前系武汉市中心医院眼科医师。
Li Wenliang, male and Manchu born in October 1985, a member of the Communist Party of China (CPC), was born in Jinzhou, Liaoning Province. He died on February 7, 2020 of pneumonia caused by a new coronavirus and was an ophthalmologist at Wuhan Central Hospital.
2019年12月，湖北省中西医结合医院、武汉市中心医院后湖院区、武汉市红十字会医院等陆续收治了一些不明原因肺炎病人。
In December 2019, the Hubei Province Chinese and Western Medical Association Hospital, Wuhan Central Hospital Houhu Hospital, Wuhan City Red Cross Hospital, etc. successively admitted a number of patients with unknown causes of pneumonia.
12月27日，湖北省中西医结合医院呼吸与危重症医学科主任张继先向医院报告了其接诊3例不明原因肺炎患者情况，医院将此情况上报武汉市江汉区疾控中心。
On December 27, Zhang Jixian, director of the Department of Respiratory and Critical Medicine in Hubei Province, reported three cases of unexplained pneumonia to the hospital, which reported the case to the CDC.
当天，武汉市疾控中心安排给此3例病人做了流行病学调查和检测。
On the same day, Wuhan CDC arranged for the 3 patients to do epidemiological investigation and testing.
12月29日，湖北省中西医结合医院又报告发现4例来自于华南海鲜市场的不明原因肺炎病例。
On December 29, Hubei Province, the combination of Chinese and Western medicine hospital reported four cases of unidentified pneumonia from the South China seafood market.
武汉市卫健委组织专家团队进行调查，当天晚上将相关病人转诊至武汉市金银潭医院。
Wuhan City Health Commission organized a team of experts to conduct an investigation, that night referred the relevant patients to Wuhan gold and silver pool hospital.
考虑到全市多家医院发现类似病例，武汉市卫健委分别于12月30日15时10分、18时50分在系统内下发部门文件《关于报送不明原因肺炎救治情况的紧急通知》《关于做好不明原因肺炎救治工作的紧急通知》，要求做好不明原因肺炎救治工作，全面开展华南海鲜市场相关肺炎病例搜索和回顾性调查。
Taking into account similar cases found in many hospitals in the city, the Wuhan Health Commission issued the sectoral paper Emergency Notice on Handling Unexplained Pneumonia at 15: 10 p.m. and 18: 50 p.m. on December 30 respectively.
该两份通知分别于当天15时22分和19时许被人上传到互联网上。
The notifications were uploaded to the Internet at approximately 1522 and 1900 hours, respectively.
2019年12月30日17时30分左右，李文亮医生收到同事发给他的信息，17时43分，李文亮医生以“李文亮　武汉　眼科”昵称在微信群“武汉大学临床04级”中转发、发布“华南水果海鲜市场确诊了7例SARS”“在我们医院后湖院区急诊科隔离”等文字信息和1张标有“SARS冠状病毒检出〈高置信度〉阳性指标”等字样的临床病原体筛查结果图片、1段时长11秒的肺部CT视频。
On December 30, 2019, at around 17: 30, Dr. Lee Wenliang received a message from his colleagues. At 17: 43, Dr. Lee Wenliang, nicknamed "Li Wenliang Wuhan Eye" in the micro-faith group "Wuhan University Clinical 04" and a picture of clinical pathogen screening results marked "SARS coronavirus detection positive index," 1 11-second lung CT video.
18时42分，又在该群发布“最新消息是，冠状病毒感染确定了，正在进行病毒分型”“大家不要外传，让家人亲人注意防范”。
At 1842 hours, the group again released "The latest news is that coronavirus infection has been confirmed and a virus is being typed."
同时，类似信息也出现在其他微信群中。
At the same time, similar information appears in other micromessage groups.
被人上传到网上的武汉市卫健委两份部门文件，与李文亮医生等人转发、发布的信息，引发关注和讨论。
Upload on the website of Wuhan City Health Commission two departmental documents, and Dr. Li Wenliang and others forward, published information, attracted attention and discussion.
二、李文亮医生接受公安机关谈话、训诫和医院谈话情况2019年12月31日13时38分，武汉市卫健委发布《关于当前我市肺炎疫情的情况通报》说，“已发现27例病例”“上述病例系病毒性肺炎”，并称“到目前为止调查未发现明显人传人现象，未发现医务人员感染”。
At 13: 38 p.m. on December 31, 2019, the Wuhan Health Protection Commission issued a "briefing on the current situation of pneumonia in our city," saying "27 cases have been found" "The case is viral pneumonia," adding that "investigations have so far found no evidence of human-to-human transmission and no infection by medical personnel."
多家媒体对此进行了报道。
This was reported in several media outlets.
按照武汉市关于不明原因肺炎疫情防控工作安排，武汉市公安机关依据传染病防治、治安管理等法律法规，以及市卫健委的情况通报，对在网上出现的转发、发布SARS等传染病信息情况进行了调查处置。
In accordance with Wuhan city's arrangements for the prevention and control of pneumonia due to unknown causes, the Wuhan public security organs have investigated and dealt with the situation of transmitting and publishing information on SARS and other infectious diseases on the basis of the laws and regulations on the prevention and control of infectious diseases, public security administration and the notice of the municipal health committee.
2020年1月3日13时30分左右，武汉市公安局武昌分局中南路派出所与李文亮医生联系后，李文亮医生在同事陪同下来到该派出所。
On 3 January 2020, at about 1330 hours, Dr. Wenliang Li was escorted to the police station by his colleagues after the Wuhan Public Security Bureau Wuchang Branch Zhongnan Road Police Station contacted Dr. Li Wenliang.
派出所副所长杨某安排负责内勤的民警胡某与李文亮医生谈话。
Police station deputy director Yang arrangements in charge of the internal affairs of Hu Mou and Dr. Lee Wenliang talk.
经谈话核实后，谈话人员现场制作了笔录。
After verification of the interview, the interviewee took notes on the spot.
李文亮医生表示，在微信群中发有关SARS的信息是不对的，以后会注意的，谈话人员对李文亮医生制作了训诫书。
Dr Lee said it was wrong to send messages about SARS in a microphone group. As will be noticed later, the interviewer made a sermon to Dr Liang.
李文亮医生亦持有1份训诫书，于14时30分许离开派出所。
Dr Lee Man-liang also held a reprimand and left the station at about 1430 hours.
谈话人员为内勤民警胡某和1名辅警，胡某在训诫书上签上了自己的名字和当天值班民警徐某的名字。
Interlocutors for the internal police Hu Mou and a police auxiliaries, Hu in the sermon signed his name and the day of the police on duty Xu Mou name.
实际上，徐某未参加谈话。
In fact, Xu did not participate in the conversation.
此前，李文亮医生在微信群里发的信息被人在互联网上大量转发之后，2019年12月31日上午，武汉市中心医院有关领导和李文亮医生进行了谈话。
Earlier, Dr. Li Wenliang in the micro-group of messages were widely relayed on the Internet, on the morning of December 31, 2019, Wuhan City Central Hospital leaders and Dr. Lee Wenliang talked.
李文亮医生在谈话中表示，他把未经核实的有关SARS等信息转发到同学群中，目的是提醒群内同学注意防范。
During the conversation, Dr. Lee said he relayed unverified information about SARS to his classmates to remind them to guard against SARS.
医院让李文亮医生写一份认识材料。
The hospital asked Dr. Li Wenliang to write an awareness material.
至李文亮医生生病住院前，其一直在医院眼科医师岗位照常工作。
Dr Lee remained in the hospital as an ophthalmologist until he became ill in hospital.
三、李文亮医生发病、治疗、抢救情况2020年1月10日，李文亮医生出现发热，1月12日入住武汉市中心医院眼科病房，1月14日转入呼吸与危重症医学科三病区，1月23日转入呼吸与危重症医学科重症监护室，2月7日不幸去世。
On January 10, 2020, Dr. Li Wenliang developed fever. On January 12, he was admitted to the ophthalmology ward of Wuhan Central Hospital. On January 14, he was transferred to the Department of Respiratory and Critical Medicine.
2019年12月9日，李文亮医生从眼科门诊轮转到眼科病房工作。
On 9 December 2019, Dr. Lee was transferred from the ophthalmological clinic to the ophthalmology ward.
2020年1月6日，李文亮医生收治了一名82岁的眼病患者。
On January 6, 2020, Dr. Li Wenliang admitted an 82-year-old eye patient.
该患者1月7日发热，后确诊感染新冠病毒，于1月23日病逝。
The patient developed fever on January 7, was diagnosed with the new crown virus, and died on January 23.
1月10日，李文亮医生开始发热，在武汉市中心医院发热门诊就诊。
On January 10, Dr. Wenliang began to get feverish and went to the fever clinic of Wuhan Central Hospital.
1月12日，李文亮医生在武汉市中心医院眼科二区住院，入院诊断为右眼急性结膜炎、肺部感染。
On January 12, Dr. Li Wenliang was hospitalized in the ophthalmologic section of Wuhan Central Hospital. He was admitted to hospital with acute conjunctivitis of the right eye and pulmonary infection.
1月14日，李文亮医生双肺感染加重，转入呼吸三区病房。
On January 14, Dr. Lee Wenliang increased his lung infection and moved to the respiratory ward.
呼吸三区安排李文亮医生住单间隔离，组织专人轮班护理，即时监测血氧饱和度、心率、血压，给予呼吸支持和抗病毒、抗感染、化痰、护胃等对症支持治疗，使用激素和丙种球蛋白。
Respiratory area 3 area arranges Dr. Li Wenliang to live alone, organizes specially trained personnel to work shifts, monitors blood oxygen saturation, heart rate, blood pressure, gives respiratory support and symptomatic support treatment such as antiviral, anti-infective, sputum and stomach care, uses hormones and gamma globulin.
1月15日至1月18日，根据李文亮医生的病情，主诊医生适时调整有关药物和治疗方式。
From January 15 to January 18, according to Dr. Lee Wenliang's illness, attending doctors timely adjust the relevant drugs and treatment.
1月19日，李文亮医生间断发热。
On January 19, Dr. Li Wenliang had a discontinuous fever.
下午，医院呼吸与危重症医学科主任医师、新冠肺炎院内医疗救治专家组组长查看李文亮医生病情，提出治疗意见。
In the afternoon, the chief physician of hospital breathing and critical medicine, the group leader of hospital medical treatment group of Xinguan Pneumonia, consulted Dr.
当晚，医院请华中科技大学同济医院呼吸与危重症医学科教授、武汉市新冠肺炎救治专家组组长为李文亮医生会诊。
In the evening, the hospital invited Dr. Li Wenliang, Professor of Respiratory and Critical Medicine of Tongji Hospital of Huazhong University of Science and Technology and Head of Wuhan New Crown Pneumonia Treatment Team.
1月20日至22日，李文亮医生没有发热，但喘气症状仍然较重。
From 20 to 22 January, Dr. Liang did not experience fever, but his asthma symptoms remained severe.
1月15日、19日、20日、21日，新冠肺炎院内医疗救治专家组组长、副组长等院内专家多次查看李文亮医生病情并提出诊疗意见。
On January 15, 19, 20 and 21, hospital experts such as the head and vice-group leader of the hospital's medical treatment group repeatedly checked Dr. LiWenliang's condition and offered medical advice.
1月22日23时50分许，李文亮医生如厕后出现喘气、呼吸困难等症状，血氧饱和度下降至88%，经治疗后症状稍缓解。
At about 2350 hours on January 22, Dr Liang developed symptoms such as wheezing and shortness of breath after using the toilet. Blood oxygen saturation decreased to 88%.
主诊医生再次告知其病情较重，征得其同意后，于1月23日凌晨3时30分许将李文亮医生转入重症监护室。
The attending physician again informed him of the seriousness of his condition and, with his consent, transferred Dr. Li Wenliang to the intensive care unit at about 3.30 a.m. on 23 January.
1月27日以前，武汉市包括市中心医院在内的多数医院不具备核酸检测资质和条件。
Prior to January 27, most hospitals in Wuhan, including the downtown hospital, did not have nucleic acid test qualifications and conditions.
经设施改造升级后，1月27日武汉市中心医院开始试运行核酸检测。
After upgrading the facilities, the test run of nucleic acid was started in Wuhan Central Hospital on January 27.
1月28日、1月31日，医院先后两次对李文亮医生做了核酸检测，第一次结果为阴性，第二次结果为阳性。
On January 28 and January 31, the hospital tested Dr. Li Wenliang on two separate tests for nucleic acid, the first negative and the second positive.
1月31日，李文亮医生确诊感染新冠病毒。
On January 31, Dr. Lee Wenliang confirmed the infection with the new crown virus.
1月31日至2月3日，李文亮医生无发热，呼吸急促有一定缓解，但精神、食欲欠佳。
From January 31 to February 3, Dr. Lee Wenliang no fever, shortness of breath has some relief, but the spirit, appetite is poor.
2月4日中午，出现呕吐，咳嗽频繁，伴喘息加重，经治疗后症状缓解。
At noon on 4 February, vomiting, frequent coughing, aggravated wheezing and relief after treatment occurred.
2月5日，李文亮医生无发热，但静息状态下仍有喘息、气促，床边胸片提示右侧肺炎加重。
On February 5, Dr. Li Wenliang had no fever, but he was still gasping and shortness of breath in a state of rest.
2月6日，李文亮医生肺部病变严重，且病情有进一步恶化风险。
On 6 February, Dr. Liang had severe lung lesions and was at risk of further deterioration.
经院内专家组会诊，建议转到条件更为专业的后湖院区，经征得李文亮医生及其家属同意后，于18时20分许，由主诊医生和两名护士陪护李文亮医生转院区。
After consultation with the hospital team, it was recommended to transfer to the more professional Houhu district. At about 18.20, the attending doctor and two nurses accompanied Dr. Lee Man-liang to the hospital area with the consent of Dr. Lee Man-liang and his family.
18时55分许，到达武汉市中心医院后湖院区。
About 18: 55, arrived in Wuhan city central hospital back lake courtyard area.
2月6日19时20分，李文亮医生出现神志模糊，心率、血压进行性下降，立即推注肾上腺素强心，开放血管通道积极补液扩容提升血压。
On February 6, 19: 20, Dr. Lee Wenliang appeared dizzy, heart rate, blood pressure gradually declined, immediately push adrenaline strong heart, open blood vessel positive fluid expansion to raise blood pressure.
同时进行气管插管，有创呼吸机维持呼吸，持续胸外按压。
At the same time, endotracheal intubation, invasive breathing machine to maintain breathing, continuous chest compressions.
21时30分，上体外心肺复苏仪，辅助持续胸外心脏按压，继续进行心肺复苏抢救，并给予积极的药物复苏。
At 2130 hours, cardiopulmonary resuscitation (cardiopulmonary resuscitation) was performed, assisted by continuous extracorporeal cardiopulmonary resuscitation (CPR), and positive drug resuscitation was given.
22时40分许，使用医院从武汉亚心医院借来的ECMO（体外膜肺氧合机，俗称“人工肺”）对李文亮医生进行治疗。
At about 2240 hours, Dr. Li was treated with ECMO (External Membrane Pulmonary Oxygen, commonly known as "Artificial Lung") borrowed from Wuhan Yaxin Hospital.
经武汉市卫健委协调，北京协和医院专家赶到抢救现场。
Wuhan city health committee coordination, Beijing Concorde hospital experts rushed to the rescue site.
2月7日凌晨2时58分，李文亮医生心电图呈直线反应，宣告临床死亡。
On February 7, at 2: 58 a.m., Dr. Lee Wenliang electrocardiogram in a linear response, the announcement of clinical death.
3时48分，医院发布了李文亮医生去世的消息。
At 0348 hours, the hospital announced the death of Dr. Li Wenliang.
组织抢救的医生说，李文亮医生是我们的同事，又很年轻，我们不希望他走，只要有一点希望我们就不愿放弃，当时没有想其他任何因素，就是想救活他，所以抢救了很长时间。
Dr. Li Wenliang was our colleague and very young, and we didn't want him to go. We didn't want to give up if there was one thing we wanted, 'said the doctor who organized the rescue.
李文亮医生的主诊医生表示，虽然没能挽回李文亮医生的生命，但对他的治疗是规范的，抢救是及时的，大家尽了最大努力。
Dr. Lee Wenliang's attending doctor said that although did not save the life of Dr. Li Wenliang, but his treatment is standardized, rescue is timely, everyone did their best.
据为李文亮医生会诊的院外专家讲，从李文亮医生病案看，医院治疗比较规范，能够根据病情调整药物和措施。
According to the non-hospital experts consulted by Dr. Li Wenliang, the hospital treatment is more standardized and can adjust the medication and measures according to the patient's condition.
医院建议采取和实际采取的重要医疗措施，均征求了李文亮医生或其家属意见。
Dr. Lee or his family were consulted on the important medical measures recommended and actually taken by the hospital.
四、李文亮医生去世后抚恤、善后情况李文亮医生不幸去世后，武汉市中心医院成立工作专班，全面负责抚恤、善后工作。
After the tragic death of Dr. Li Wenliang, a special class was set up in Wuhan Central Hospital to be fully responsible for compensation and rehabilitation work.
2月7日下午，市中心医院领导分别探望慰问了李文亮医生的父母、妻子和孩子。
On the afternoon of February 7, the head of the downtown hospital visited Dr. Lee's parents, wife and children respectively.
应李文亮医生妻子的要求，安排她和孩子在有关医院进行休养。
At the request of Dr. Lee's wife, arrangements were made for her and her children to recuperate at the relevant hospital.
经武汉市中心医院申请，武汉市人力资源和社会保障局已认定李文亮医生为工伤。
Wuhan city by the application of the central hospital, Wuhan Human Resources and Social Security Bureau has identified Dr. Lee Wenliang as an industrial injury.
根据有关规定，目前已全额发放了工亡补助金，核发了丧葬补助金。
In accordance with the relevant regulations, death and disability benefits have been paid in full and funeral grants have been granted.
保险公司已向李文亮医生家属赔付了捐赠保险（针对抗击新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情的一线医护人员）。
The insurance company has paid Dr. Liang's family a donation of insurance (for front-line health workers fighting the new coronavirus-infected pneumonia).
武汉市中心医院工会号召职工为李文亮医生及其家属进行了捐款，武汉市红十字会收到了定向爱心捐款，以上捐款均已转交李文亮医生家属。
The trade union of Wuhan Central Hospital called on the staff to make a donation to Dr. Li Wenliang and his family.
3月4日，国家卫健委等部门印发决定，表彰全国卫生健康系统新冠肺炎疫情防控工作先进个人，其中有李文亮医生。
On March 4, the State Health Commission and other departments issued a decision to recognize advanced individuals, including Dr. Li Wenliang, in the prevention and control of the new crown pneumonia epidemic in the national health system.
五、工作建议由于中南路派出所出具训诫书不当，执法程序不规范，调查组已建议湖北省武汉市监察机关对此事进行监督纠正，督促公安机关撤销训诫书并追究有关人员责任，及时向社会公布处理结果。
V. PROPOSALS FOR WORK Because of improper issuing of reprimands and irregular law enforcement procedures at the Central and South Road Police Station, the investigation group has advised the Wuhan Municipal Supervision Bureau in Hubei Province to supervise and correct the matter, urge the public security organs to revoke the reprimand and investigate the responsibility of the personnel concerned.
国家监委调查组　　2020年3月19日    来源：新华社推荐阅读▼国际公共卫生专家：美国疫情防控迎来转折点，未来几周病例会迅速上升你知道现在最火本科专业是什么吗？学还是不学，这是个问题揍他可以。
